        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>92/93/9400 Series vehicles, built after February 2, 1996, are produced with Stainless steel hood
                    rub plates (
                    <hotlnk xrefid="f9609011">Figure 1</hotlnk>). These plates are available for vehicles built before
                    February 2, 1996. Stainless steel rub plates mounted on the inside of the hood, on both sides, will
                    eliminate the squeaking noise caused by the fiberglass hood rubbing against the plastic cowl mounted
                    rub blocks, and stop the wear pattern on the inside of the hood from the rub blocks. The stainless
                    steel hood rub plates may also reduce stress and cracks on the outer surface of the hood in this
                    area. This TSI contains parts and service information to install stainless steel rub plates on
                    92/93/9400 Series vehicles built before February 2, 1996.
                </para>
                <figure id="f9609011" figsize="col-wide">
                    <graphic filename="../tsifigures/G9609011.webp" type="webp" resolution="150"/>
                    <caption>Figure 1.</caption>
                </figure>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
